data.description: Welcome to this inviting tri-level home that's now on the market! Boasting three bedrooms and two full baths, this residence is adorned with new flooring and fresh paint, providing a welcoming ambiance.   ***This home is VA assumable. Step inside to discover modern comforts, including recently updated kitchen with granite, backsplash, new sink and fridge.  The kitchen has a lovely space for a breakfast/ dining space with door that opens up to the deck.   Also, beautifully updated bathrooms and a brand-new HVAC system with new ducts, with a new wifi thermostat,  ensuring a cozy and efficient living environment. Recessed lighting has been added throughout the home.   An entire new electrical panel was professionally installed.  Roof has been checked.   A new chimney cap was installed.   Enjoy the lovely family room with a cozy wood burning fireplace to warm up to in the winter!   Upper level has 3 spacious bedrooms, full bath, kitchen and family room.  The entire home has been recently painted, and new/ newer flooring.  The beautiful carpet was just installed.  The lower level of the house is dedicated to entertainment, featuring a spacious recreation room complete with a mini bar, making it the ideal spot for gatherings and relaxation. Additionally, you'll find a convenient laundry area, adding functionality to your daily routine. This meticulously upgraded property offers the added benefit of a VA assumable loan, simplifying the financing process for eligible buyers. The large deck beckons you to step outside and enjoy the fresh air while taking in the view of the newly fenced yard, equipped with two gates for easy access. Whether you're hosting a barbecue or simply unwinding, this deck provides the perfect outdoor retreat. The spacious driveway is a practical feature, accommodating 4-6 vehicles with ease, ensuring that parking is never a concern. To cater to your storage needs, there's also a storage building on the property, providing ample space for your belongings. No HOA!  One of the standout features of this home is the absence of homeowners' association (HOA) fees, offering you the freedom to enjoy your property without additional monthly expenses or restrictions Seize the opportunity to make this beautifully upgraded house your home. With its blend of modern amenities, entertaining spaces, and outdoor charm, it's a residence that truly caters to a comfortable and enjoyable lifestyle. Don't miss out on the chance to call this place yours!
